
# Day 16 — Ansible Roles, DynamoDB, StatefulSet, Service Check

## 🔹 Ansible — Create Role Structure

# Students must create:
# roles/
#   pathnex/
#     tasks/main.yml
#     handlers/main.yml
#     templates/
#     vars/main.yml

#roles/pathnex/tasks/main.yml
---
- name: Install httpd
  yum:
    name: httpd
    state: present
- name: Copy index template
  template:
    src: index.html.j2
    dest: /var/www/html/index.html
  notify: Restart httpd
- name: Start and enable httpd
  service:
    name: httpd
    state: started
    enabled: yes


#roles/pathnex/handlers/main.yml

---
- name: Restart httpd
  service:
    name: httpd
    state: restarted

#roles/pathnex/vars/main.yml

---

package_name: httpd
service_name: httpd
web_root: /var/www/html

